Package purchasable

Class Purchasable

java.lang.Object
purchasable.Purchasable
All Implemented Interfaces:
HasImage
Direct Known Subclasses:
Item, Monster
public abstract class Purchasable extends Object implements HasImage
The Purchasable class gives other classes the ability to be purchased from the shop and gives additional info to be displayed in the store. This class implements the HasImage class so it can be displayed visually in the GUI.
Author:
Bede Nathan, Celia Allen
